
    The Network Simulator, Versão 3.19
    --------------------------------

To run NS-3, just follow these steps:

Clone the repo with:
git clone git@github.com:otaviobertucini/mptcp-ns3.git

Enter in the file you just cloned:
cd mptcp-ns3

To build NS-3:
./waf configure --enable-tests --enable-examples && ./waf build

To run the simulations:
cd scratch
./waf --run "scratch/my_mptcp --attackerOn=true" to run the simulation with the attacker
./waf --run "scratch/my_mptcp --attackerOn=false" para rodar a simulação without the attacker

More info can be found in:
http://www.nsnam.org
